          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33474315/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33474315/" class="">第54页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59186820/" class=" " title="SincerelyYours">SincerelyYours</a>
                (People do things for a reason)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33474315">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">生命本性是在无止境地向上奋进；是在争取生命力之扩大，再扩大（图存、传种，盖所以不断扩大）；争取灵活，再灵活；争取自由，再自由。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-11-20 21:24</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>生命本性是在无止境地向上奋进；是在争取生命力之扩大，再扩大（图存、传种，盖所以不断扩大）；争取灵活，再灵活；争取自由，再自由。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







